Class TabConfigDependentBOMImpl

All Implemented Interfaces:
BusinessObjectModule, DependentBOM
public class TabConfigDependentBOMImpl
extends BusinessObjectModuleImpl
implements DependentBOM

This is the Dependent Business Object Module implementation for a Tab Configuration BOM. A Tab Configuration BOM consists of the .tab file and its associated .properties file. Both are stored on the database in the AppResource table. This class is responsible for determining the dependencies that exist for a Tab Configuration BOM.
